Farlin Baby Chair - Normal (Pink) Price: Rs.1850

Does your little one have to adjust to oversized chairs at home? Make him feel comfortable with the Farlin Baby Chair. This chair from Farlin is made of the PVC and if offers adequate support to your little angel’s body. Suitable for children from the age of 12 months this Farlin Baby Chair has a low height to suit your tiny tot. The strong and sturdy legs of the Farlin Baby Chair can hold up to the weight of 25 kg.

When you seat your child the chair makes a sound that will not only excite your baby but also encourage them to sit on by herself on her own little chair. Sitting in an individual chair will boost the confidence of your little one. With the Baby Chair from Farlin your young toddler will not have to feel awkward on outsized chairs.
